                            <span class="block w-10 h-10 p-2.5 bg-white text-gray-500 shadow-md ring-1 ring-gray-100 rounded transition group-hover/link:shadow-sm dark:text-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:ring-gray-600">
